headline: Fastenal and RFK Racing Celebrate 15 Years of NASCAR Partnership
summary: WINONA, Minn., January 08, 2025--RFK Racing and primary partner Fastenal Company (Nasdaq: FAST) will celebrate their 15th season of partnership in 2025. Fastenal, which recently extended its relationship with RFK, is one of the longest-tenured brands in NASCAR. When Fastenal initially teamed up with RFK in 2010, they were paired with NASCAR Hall of Fame driver Carl Edwards.
